steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"49q40","text":"1. Study design","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"1qvio","text":"An anonymous self-administered questionnaire was deployed online using Google form.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"9duc4","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"8aand","text":"2. Settings and participants","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"4gmtl","text":"Data were collected between 15th October, 2021 and 15th December, 2021.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"2mu52","text":"Currently pharmacy students are studying at public or private university in Bangladesh.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"8ctgi","text":"Online link was sent to 1090 Bangladeshi university pharmacy students via social media networks or personal emails.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"9rjo9","text":"Ethical Review Committee approved this study as exempt.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"6kp09","text":"There was no external funding for the study.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"7hc32","text":"No clinical experiments were conducted on the subjects and the individual was free to reject participation at any time.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"d50lg","text":"3. Participant’s inclusion criteria","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"eivl3","text":"Participants clearly understand and consent with the research objectives.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"5db8u","text":"Willing to provide anonymous data on COVID-19 vaccine and vaccinations.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"7qa04","text":"Pharmacy students of public or private universities in Bangladesh.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"826di","text":"Studying in junior (1st year) to masters, and research degree level.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"doi4s","text":"4. Measures and survey instruments development","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"ndf3","text":"Potential factors associated with COVID-19 vaccine acceptance and hesitancy has been conceptualized from recent reviews on topics.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"2jfvs","text":"Multi-items questionnaire was adopted from theory analysis of the recent studies reflected COVID-19 vaccinations among the various students’ sub-groups globally.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"91ufn","text":"Employed 5-point Likert scale: “definitely yes”, “yes probably”, “unsure”, “probably not” and “definitely not” to assess the in-depth intention.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"p8hp","text":"Instrument was developed in bilingually and pre-tested on 20 student pharmacists.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"5br8d","text":"Survey instrument assessed (1) participants socio-demographic profile; (2) COVID-19 vaccine acceptance intention, (3) potential drivers of COVID-19 vaccine","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"d404p","text":"1. Study design","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ah60d","text":"4. Measures and survey instruments development","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"f8gg7","text":"3. Participant’s inclusion criteria","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"9ud6t","text":"2. Settings and participants","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"2r7h2","text":"acceptance and hesitancy, and (4) willingness to pay (WTP) for vaccines.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"b2uig","text":"5. Survey administration","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"647av","text":"Convenience sampling technique was used for systematic data gathering from online survey tools.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"18kbn","text":"The investigators distributed the online questionnaire among pharmacy students in almost all universities and encouraged them to participate in this study.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"d7gqp","text":"6. Study variables","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"3trjt","text":"“Vaccine acceptance intent” was the single outcome variable evaluated in binary response (1=Yes, 0=No).","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"7mqge","text":"Response for independent variables were dichotomized into (1=Yes, 0=No).","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"7mgot","text":"We used one item question to understand WTP and responses were measure by 1=Yes and 0=No scale.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"ffues","text":"7. Sample size calculation","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"24nff","text":"For observational studies, a data of minimum of 500 considered the sample size compulsory to conduct binary logistic regression that characterizes the variable parameters.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"47nm5","text":"The survey bars showed receiving any partial data, which ensured collection of complete response.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"eva3o","text":"8. Statistical analysis","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"6oqii","text":"Raw data were inserted into the Microsoft excel (version 10).","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"1s739","text":"Statistical Package of Social Science (SPSS) software IBM-SPSS (version 25) was used for complete data analysis (IBM SPSS Statistics, RRID: SCR_016479.).","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"clve1","text":"Binary regression analysis was employed to ascertain the association mode between independent variable and outcome variable.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"9lu9p","text":"1034 data were finally analyzed to rationalize the study objectives.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"8hgp9","text":"The study considered p\u003c0.05 as statistically significant cut-point value.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
